div.p: JioStar tackled rapid traffic surges and optimized performance testing, handling 30M+ concurrent users with Gatling Enterprise, ensuring zero downtime during IPL matches.
Sonepar optimized e-commerce performance with Gatling Enterprise, simulating 720 virtual users for unmatched speed and scalability.
Popken Fashion Group achieved a flawless cloud migration and skyrocketed e-commerce performance with Gatling Enterprise—5,000 users, 100k+ requests!
Korem skyrocketed user capacity, crushed system crashes, and supercharged performance with Gatling Enterprise—transforming their platform!
TUI boosted real-time performance by 50% with Gatling Enterprise, transforming scalability, automation, and response times for ultimate efficiency.
TRAY improved their POS system with Gatling Enterprise, achieving 90% faster response times and supporting 20,000 users, enhancing efficiency and scalability.
Learn how Interdiscount used Gatling Enterprise to ensure website stability and performance during peak traffic seasons like Black Friday and Cyber Monday.
How an AI company used Gatling Enterprise to enhance performance infrastructure.
How a scaleup ensured performance, avoided crashes, and managed high user volume with Gatling Enterprise.
Unveiling a leading e-commerce company’s performance testing journey: ensuring stability amidst bot challenges.
Discover how Gatling Enterprise became a key component in the airline’s new agile shift-left model.
See how SNCF Connect & Tech moved to the Cloud and fostered a thriving community with Gatling Enterprise.
Discover how an NGO handles event ticketing with Gatling Enterprise.
